      <title>七＆amp;我的指导小姐在收购竞标中增加了压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/seven-i-s-guidance-miss-adds-to-pressure-amid-takeover-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七＆amp; I Holdings Co.预测了当年缺少分析师估计的本年度运营利润和收入，这增加了公司在剥离超市和银行单位股份后寻找新的增长途径的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/seven-i-s-guidance-miss-adds-to-pressure-amid-takeover-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 06:59:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库“火出售”在全球范围内发送长期收益率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来自较长日期的美国国债的出埃及进出加速了，这加剧了自2020年以来最大的抛售，这本来应该是世界上最安全的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 05:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼卢比瀑布在关税紧张局势中记录低的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/indonesian-rupiah-falls-to-historic-low-as-tariff-tension-bites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚的卢比亚（Rupiah）兑美元的历史降至最低，因为市场参与者的价格为全球贸易摩擦的影响，促使另一家中央银行的干预。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/indonesian-rupiah-falls-to-historic-low-as-tariff-tension-bites</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 03:42:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
