      <title>CK和Hutchison分享了自巴拿马港口交易以来的所有收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/ck-hutchison-shares-erase-all-gains-since-panama-ports-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd股票在周三延长下降，自该公司同意上个月将其巴拿马运河港口资产出售给Blackrock Inc.领导的财团以来，消除了所有预付款。]]></description>
